<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <link href="/public/css/requestMeal.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav')%>

    <div class="container-fluid" style="padding: 7%;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6 px-5">
                <div class="con">
                    <h2 class="heading my-4" style="display:block;">Request a Helping Hand: Meals, Deliveries</h2>
                    <p>
                        We have a whole group of your neighbors waiting to help you get the food and support that you
                        need.
                        <b>Here’s how it works:</b>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Fill out this form to tell us what you need.</li>
                            <li>We’ll do our best to match your request with an available volunteer.</li>
                            <li>We’ll get in touch to confirm delivery date.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                    <h3>We have a few offerings:</h3>
                    <p class="mx-4">
                        <h3>For Free Meals</h3>
                        <p class="my-4">Free meals are available for the people who can not afford the essential stuffs
                            on the daily
                            basis due to lockdown.</p>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mx-4">
                        <h3>For Deliveries</h3>
                        <p class="my-4">Request groceries, supplies,medicines, or other essential deliveries. We will
                            confirm your
                            request and
                            then connect you by phone
                            with your volunteer. The two of you will coordinate a delivery day, time, and payment method
                            from there.</p>
                    </p>
                    <img src="/public/images/delivery.png" style="width:450px;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
                <div class="con">
                    <h2 class="heading my-4" style="display:block;">Please fill out the delivery details:</h2>
                    <p>All other services rely on volunteers with limited availability. We’ll work to get you deliveries
                        as soon
                        as possible
                        but please be patient with us–it can take a couple days to a week to schedule your first grocery
                        or
                        other delivery.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <%- include('forms/request-meal-form')%>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="signup-text my-5" style="color: #838181e6;">
            <p style="margin-top:9%;text-align: center;">We take your privacy very seriously. We only collect this data
                to
                help
                us meet the
                goals of Neighbor Express
                and match
                you with someone who has requested aid in your local community. Please contact us at
                rishabhjain.1936@gmail.com with any
                questions or requests to be removed from the list.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.onload = function highlightClass() {
            let navItems = document.getElementsByClassName('nav-item');
            let nav = document.getElementsByTagName('nav');

            for (let i = 0; i < navItems.length; ++i) {
                if (navItems[i].innerText == "Request Meal") navItems[i].classList.add("active")
            }
            nav[0].classList.remove("navbar-light", "bg-transparent")
            nav[0].classList.add("navbar-dark", "bg-primary")
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>